OL,5, The British Museum has struck a #50m   
OL,6, deal with energy giant BP to help fund 
OL,7, a major renovation programme.          
OL,9,FThe 10-year agreement was announced    
OL,10,Falongside plans to upgrade a third of  
OL,11,Fthe museum's galleries and "phase out" 
OL,12,Fits reliance on fossil fuels.          
OL,14,FThe relationship with BP dates back to 
OL,15,F1996 and climate campaigners have long 
OL,16,Fcriticised the decision to to take     
OL,17,Fmoney from an oil and gas firm.        
OL,19,FOne group branded the new deal "out of 
OL,20,Ftouch" and "completely indefensible".  
